There is nothing like a pool which is set high on a cliff, with a view out over the sea, and one of the prettiest is the pool of @monasterosantarosa 
be sure to view this in reels for the full effect and be sure to tag someone who would love this 💙
Wishing everyone a great Saturday ! 
 
Video by @monasterosantarosa •
